  {"id": "US-012", "title": "Contact Page", "description": "Build /contact page with split layout desktop (form left 60%, info right 40%) / centered single column mobile. Contact form: firstName + lastName row, email field, subject field, message textarea, submit button full-width (Gönder). Real-time validation on blur: firstName/lastName (2-50 chars, letters only), email (valid format), subject (5-200 chars), message (20-2000 chars). Form states: idle, validating (inline errors), submitting (button loading, form disabled), success (toast + form reset + Teşekkürler message), error (toast + inline errors + retry). Info section: email mailto link with icon, location Türkiye (Europe/Istanbul), social links, availability status green dot.", "acceptanceCriteria": ["Split layout: form left 60% / info right 40% desktop, stacked mobile", "Form fields: firstName + lastName side-by-side, email full-width, subject full-width, message textarea rows-6", "Field styling: bg-background-elevated, border-border, focus border-primary ring-primary/20, rounded-md", "Validation on blur: firstName lastName require 2-50 chars letters-only, email valid format required, subject 5-200 chars required, message 20-2000 chars required", "Error display: text-error text-sm below field, border-error on field", "Submit button: w-full bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white font-semibold, text Gönder", "Submitting state: button shows spinner + text, all fields disabled", "Success state: toast success + form reset + message", "Error state: toast error + inline error message + fields retain data", "Info section: email icon + mailto link, location icon + text, social icons row, availability dot + text", "Responsive: single column stacked on mobile", "Typecheck passes", "Tests for contact page pass"], "depends_on": ["US-004", "US-005"], "screens": ["0539313873cb412d9d0b86ff0961a9ef"]},
